data.description: *Assumable 2.99% VA loan. Veteran status not required to qualify. Call for details* Every day is a vacation when you come home to “A Richards Built Home” mountain retreat. This well-appointed log home delivers Tahoe mountain living at its best. All-season slate entry is perfect for snowy boots or sandy feet straight from the beach. 3 bdrms/2 bathrooms on main level w/ direct access to covered deck & hot tub. Upstairs an open concept living/dining/kitchen space is beautifully anchored by a 2-sided stone fireplace. Large windows provide natural light & a sense of being in the treetops. Spacious deck perfect for entertaining & enjoying peace & quiet in the backyard. Primary suite w/ private balcony overlooking the canyon below & Diamond Peak in the distance. 2 car garage w/ epoxy floor & level driveway. Located on school bus route with “priority” snow removal providing clear winter roads. Ski resorts, beaches, hiking trails & golf nearby. IVGID amenities incl private beach access & more.
